'''不丹-以色列关系'''是指[[以色列国|以色列国]]与[[不丹王国|不丹王国]]之间的外交关系。随着不、以双方驻印度大使签署公报，不丹于2020年12月正式承认以色列国并与其建立外交关系。<ref>{{Cite web|last=staff|first=T. O. I.|title=Israel inks deal establishing diplomatic relations with Bhutan|url=https://www.timesofisrael.com/israel-inks-deal-establishing-diplomatic-relations-with-bhutan/|access-date=2020-12-15|website=www.timesofisrael.com|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219141840/https://www.timesofisrael.com/israel-inks-deal-establishing-diplomatic-relations-with-bhutan/}}</ref>以色列是与不丹建立关系的第54个国家。<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-12-12|title=Israel, Bhutan establish formal diplomatic relations|url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/india-news/israel-bhutan-establish-formal-diplomatic-relations/story-Ipu61jdGWFXqmDrhwxmQtO.html|access-date=2020-12-15|website=Hindustan Times|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201221173649/https://www.hindustantimes.com/india-news/israel-bhutan-establish-formal-diplomatic-relations/story-Ipu61jdGWFXqmDrhwxmQtO.html}}</ref>不丹曾经在[[巴勒斯坦问题|巴勒斯坦问题]]上持支持[[巴勒斯坦解放组织|巴勒斯坦解放组织]]的立场，长期未承认以色列的[[主权国家|主权国家]]地位。但两国自2007年以后通过[[印度|印度]]进行非官方往来，<ref>{{Cite web|last=France-Presse|first=Agence|date=2020-12-12|title=Israel establishes 'formal diplomatic relations' with Bhutan|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/dec/12/israel-establishes-formal-diplomatic-relations-with-bhutan|access-date=2020-12-15|website=the Guardian|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210104223533/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/dec/12/israel-establishes-formal-diplomatic-relations-with-bhutan}}</ref>在正式宣布这一消息之前，两国已经进行了数年的秘密建交谈判。<ref>{{Cite news|last=Ayyub|first=Rami|date=2020-12-12|title=Israel and Bhutan establish diplomatic relations|language=en|work=Reuters|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/israel-bhutan-idUSKBN28M0NK|access-date=2020-12-15|archive-date=2020-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201224105347/https://www.reuters.com/article/israel-bhutan-idUSKBN28M0NK}}</ref>

